PLOT: A documentary about Soulwax: Director Saam Farahmand filmed Soulwax on

their recent international dates, capturing all the excitement, chaos and

humour of the world tour. Where the Beastie Boys filmed one gig with 50

cameras, Soulwax filmed 120 shows with one camera, in Europe, Japan, US

Latin America and Australia. The result is a snapshot of life on the road

with one of the most exciting live bands in the world, and features their

friends including 2manyDJ's, James Murphy & Nancy Whang (LCD Soundsystem)

Erol Alkan, Tiga, Justice, Busy P, So-Me, Peaches, Klaxons and many more
